Note that this change will require updating the `pom.xml` file to use the Jakarta EE API instead of the Java EE API. Specifically, the `javaee-api` dependency should be replaced with `jakartaee-api`. Additionally, the `maven-compiler-plugin` should be configured to use the Jakarta EE API. Here is an example of the updated `pom.xml` file:
